
Overview of noun evangelist

The noun evangelist has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (1) evangelist, revivalist, gospeler, gospeller -- (a preacher of the Christian gospel)
2. Evangelist -- ((when capitalized) any of the spiritual leaders who are assumed to be authors of the Gospels in the New Testament: Matthew, Mark, Luke, and John)
